The article is a statement by the President condemning a terrorist attack that took place in Bulgaria targeting Israelis. The President expresses his condolences to the families of those killed and injured and offers support to Israel, Bulgaria, and any other affected nations. He condemns the attacks on innocent civilians, including children, and pledges to stand with allies and provide assistance in identifying and bringing the perpetrators to justice. The President reaffirms the United States' commitment to Israel's security and emphasizes the friendship and solidarity between the two nations.